<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="main-content page-weekly-question">
    <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-header" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1>Weekly Question</h1>
            <p>Fresh prompts, community responses, and thoughtful discussion starters for the week ahead.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="question-layout" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="120">
            <article class="question-hero-card">
                <span class="topic-chip">This week’s prompt</span>
                <div class="weekly-visual" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <h2>What would you change first in your daily routine if you had one extra hour each week?</h2>
                <p>We’re inviting readers to reflect on small habits, creative time, and the parts of life that deserve more care. Join the discussion and share what would genuinely improve your week.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/blog/create/new" class="btn btn-primary">Write Your Take</a>
                    <a href="/blog/list" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Stories</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <aside class="question-side-card">
                <h3>Responses preview</h3>
                <div class="response-pill">“I’d protect my mornings for reading and planning.”</div>
                <div class="response-pill">“I’d make space for a long walk and quieter thinking.”</div>
                <div class="response-pill">“I’d finally learn one creative skill I’ve been postponing.”</div>
            </aside>
        </section>

        <section class="discussion-grid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="180">
            <article class="mini-card">
                <span class="topic-chip">Community insight</span>
                <h3>Readers are leaning into slower routines</h3>
                <p>Many responses highlight calm mornings, fewer notifications, and more intentional time for reflection.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="mini-card">
                <span class="topic-chip">Creative angle</span>
                <h3>Why this question matters</h3>
                <p>It opens the door to practical change, personal priorities, and how we build the kind of week we want.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="mini-card">
                <span class="topic-chip">Discussion starter</span>
                <h3>What would your ideal week look like?</h3>
                <p>Use this prompt to explore habits, energy, and the small rituals that can improve the way you create.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
